In accounting terms, these items are typically classified as "Fixed Assets" or "Property, Plant and Equipment (PP&E)". Looking at the balance sheet provided, I can see a line item called "Fixed Assets" which represents these tangible items.

From the balance sheet:
- Initial value of Fixed Assets (as of 2023-12-31): 5000000.00
- End value of Fixed Assets (as of 2024-01-28): 5352857.55

These fixed assets are the tangible items we're looking for in this task, as they represent the physical assets used in the business operations.
